result.name: Ru Chinese Restaurant

reviews.text: I ordered this set dinner for four. The food is really good and the portions are quite big, and I thought everything was going to be small and tiny. The staff could have been nicer and friendlier. The restaurant is generally quite spacious and not too crowded or loud. The overall dining experience is quite nice.
Food was delicious and good service
Tried the dim sum and soup noodles. Food quality was so so, as was the service.
Good food, expensive price

We went there for "dim sum" lunch. Food quality is "okay" not outstanding.  Staff are attentive, tables are spacious and the restaurant is not as noisy as other Chinese restaurants. Considering its price (only slightly more expensive than other local Chinese dim sum restaurant), service and cosy environment, it's still considered an ideal place for dim sum.

reviews.text: Elevator lights ( for when it arrives) is deceiving and often wrong. Food at the 9/f cafe all-you-can-eat place was quite low  quality, and in effect overpriced. Service is quite good though.

Very dirty rooms, mouldy ceilings in bathroom, I couldn't use the shower or toilet due to them being dirty, asked reception for a change of room and my request was denied, luckily I was only there for a few hours. Never again will I stop over in Hong Kong. The people and especially staff at hotel also Cathay Pacific staff at Hong Kong international airport were rude and most unhelpful people I have ever encountered in my travels. First and last time to Hong Kong.

Conditions:Clean and tidy, room is big and standard room have 2 Queen Size Bed. 
facilities available swimming pool,cafe, taxi.
High floor view is very nice. 

Location:Good,mtr 2 min walk, bus stop just beside, a31 to airport.
Serounding all market, a lot of things to shop and eat.

Was here for a vegetarian banquet and for vegetarian food, the catering was top notch. Hard to find a good hotel kitchen and chef that does vegetarian banquets this well. The vegetarian Char Siu was fantastic. The service could have been better as the wait staff seemed very inexperienced, but that doesn't take anything away from the food and the fantastic kitchen.

I was very disappointed in this hotel despite the good review the place have. The room given to us was very dirty. Bed stains, lipstick starin on curtain, dust everywhere. Our key kept blanking forcing us having to replace the keys every evening when we come back. Never had I ever written a review this bad for a hotel.

房間大，員工很熱心，不過餐飲的選擇很極端，為什麼沒有小點跟下午茶呢😳
距離各個百貨商場非常近 5ㄅ層的電梯轉換大廳也有足夠的地方給房客休息

result.name: 如粵滬中菜廳

reviews.text:
你要統得叫先知响處食乜架…………
首先介绍蒸魚，原條四斤幾都蒸得好靓。缺點係通常豉油有點淡，要加味。
其它如～牛尾煲煮到好似花膠咁，泰皇雞，素叉燒，黄🐟湯………都正
…………認真食完，我下面菜單先再評論吧………
侍應服務很好，食物好味，環境清雅。價錢不貴，性價比高。
夜景 👍🏻😍。食物質數， 非常好。😋☺
Boxing day 選擇到這裡晚餐,因為想試菜式,2019年來這裡擺結婚喜宴。㨂六人套餐,味道&服務都不錯,環境當然都好,交通亦相當方便。
食物質素可以，以酒店中菜廳來說份量較多，包房價格合理。要注意泊車優惠只限酒店門口的代客泊車，地下停車場是沒有優惠的。
